---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="About PrivacyFix - Free tools and guides to help you take back your online privacy without paying for expensive subscription services."
>
  <article class="py-12 md:py-16">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <header class="mb-12">
          <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">About PrivacyFix</h1>
          <p class="text-xl text-[var(--color-muted)]">
            Free tools and guides to take back your online privacy.
          </p>
        </header>

        <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
            Over 750 data brokers collect and sell your personal information—name, address, phone, email,
            income estimates, family members, and more. They make opting out deliberately painful, knowing
            most people will give up.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
            Paid services like DeleteMe and Incogni will handle opt-outs for you, but they cost $100-200 per year.
            That's a real barrier for many people.
          </p>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
            <strong>PrivacyFix exists to make privacy protection accessible to everyone.</strong> We provide
            free tools and step-by-step guides so you can take back control of your personal data without
            paying subscription fees.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What We Offer</h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Free Tools</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
            <li><strong>Privacy Audit:</strong> A questionnaire that creates a personalized action plan based on your risk level</li>
            <li><strong>Opt-Out Tracker:</strong> Track your progress across data brokers with 45-day follow-up reminders</li>
            <li><strong>State Rights Lookup:</strong> Find out exactly what privacy rights you have where you live</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-3">Comprehensive Guides</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
            <li>Step-by-step opt-out instructions for major data brokers</li>
            <li>State-by-state privacy law explainers</li>
            <li>California DROP portal tutorials</li>
            <li>Honest comparisons of paid vs DIY approaches</li>
          </ul>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Our Approach</h2>

          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
            <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-card)]">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-violet-500">✓</span> Honest
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">
                We're upfront that DIY takes time. If it's not right for you, we'll point you to reputable paid services.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-card)]">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-violet-500">✓</span> Privacy-First
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">
                All tools run in your browser. Your data never leaves your device. We use cookie-free analytics.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-card)]">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-violet-500">✓</span> Free
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">
                Core tools and guides are free. No paywalls, no "premium" versions, no forced sign-ups.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 rounded-xl border border-[var(--color-border)] bg-[var(--color-card)]">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-2 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-violet-500">✓</span> Transparent
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">
                We earn money through affiliate links. We clearly label them and only recommend products we'd use ourselves.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">How We Make Money</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
            PrivacyFix is funded through affiliate partnerships. When you click certain links and make a purchase,
            we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. This includes:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
            <li>VPN services (for users who want additional privacy)</li>
            <li>Identity protection services</li>
            <li>Data removal services (for users who prefer the paid route)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
            We only recommend products we believe provide genuine value. Affiliate relationships do not influence
            our content or recommendations.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
            Have questions, feedback, or suggestions? We'd love to hear from you.
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4">
            <li><strong>General:</strong> <a href="mailto:hello@getprivacyfix.com" class="text-violet-500 hover:text-violet-600">hello@getprivacyfix.com</a></li>
            <li><strong>Privacy:</strong> <a href="mailto:privacy@getprivacyfix.com" class="text-violet-500 hover:text-violet-600">privacy@getprivacyfix.com</a></li>
            <li><strong>Legal:</strong> <a href="mailto:legal@getprivacyfix.com" class="text-violet-500 hover:text-violet-600">legal@getprivacyfix.com</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Base>
